(4)
(1)
(2)
(2)
(2)
(1)
(2)
Bank of America 108
occurred and/or may only be required to make payment up to a
specified amount.
Credit derivatives are classified as investme nt and non-
investment grade based  on the credit quality of the underlying
referenced obligation. The Corporation considers ratings of BBB-
or higher as investment grade. Non-investmen t grade includes
non-rated credit derivative instruments. The Corporationdiscloses internal categ orizations of investment grade and non-
investment grade consis tent with how risk is managed for these
instruments.
