Item 9A. Controls and Procedures
Disclosure Controls and Procedures
As of the end of the period covered by this report and pursuant to
Rule 13a-15  of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended
(Exchange Act), Bank of America’ s manageme nt, including the
Chief Executive Officer and Chief Financial Officer, conducted an
evaluation of the effectiveness and design of our disclosure
controls and procedures (as that term is defin ed in Rule 13a-
15(e) of the Exchange Act). Based upon that evaluation, Bank of
America’ s Chief Execut ive Officer and Chief Financial Officer
concluded that Bank of America’ s disclosur e controls and
procedures were effective, as of the end of the period covered by
this report.
